						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">tepples wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Then what kind of addressing does it use if you define a label using an equate?</div>
<br />Some might say it depends on the value you used in the equate (variable EQU $0000 vs variable EQU $00), but I for example never define my variables like that. I use "reserve" commands to declare my variables, so that it's easier to move them around in case I want to. In that case the variables aren't assigned explicit addresses, they are relative to the last value of the PC.</div>

